*Obukla* je novu haljinu za laku noć. (She put on a new dress for the party.)

*Obući* ću belu košulju danas. (I'll wear a white shirt today.)

*Obuću* patike za trening. (I'll put on sneakers for training.)

*Obućemo* se za izlazak. (We will get dressed for going out.)

*Obući* će dete zimski kaput. (The child will put on a winter coat.)